modName: Argonian - Khajiit FabULook Eyes Stand Alone
summary: FabULook Eyes Stand Alone for Argonian & Khajiit Races offers 8 NEW Eyes Colors & Textures for BOTH Males & Females. Colors Included are Gold, Aqua, Silver, Red, Green, Pink, Violet & Blue.
descriptionHtml:
[b]FabULook Eyes Stand Alone for Argonian & Khajiit Races offers [/b][b]8 NEW [/b]Eye Colors & 7 NEW Textures (3 for Argonian and 4 for Khajiit) for BOTH Males & Females of each race. Colors Included are Gold, Aqua, Silver, Red, Green, Pink, Violet & Blue.

[b][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40960/?]ALSO THERE IS A UNIQUE EYE SET FOR INIGO THE FOLLOWER!!![/url][/b]

[color=#ff7700]This will NOT Overwrite Any Vanilla Eye Textures![/color]

I hope that you enjoy because this was a CK Nightmare for me and I will Never do it again... well maybe not never, at least not for looong while... Ok I went back added more!

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/40960/?]THANK YOU FOR INIGO by [b]Smartbluecat[/b][/url] ... My Follower For LIFE!
